title: Government expressed condolences due to terrorist attack in Ankara (Government of the Republic of Hungary) ...
text: ( Source : Government of the Republic of Hungary ) The Government of Hungary expressed its most sincere condolences to the family members of those who perished in the Ankara terrorist attack, the Ministry of Foreign Affairs and Trade informed
